Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.58,0:22:20.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}越嚼回血越是多
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.58,0:22:23.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}力量 力量 力量 力量涌现了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.64,0:22:25.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}加油啊！
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.04,0:22:26.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}我们开动吧！
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.57,0:22:29.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)}开饭啦！铛铛铛铛！
